 for the newly elected Business Agent, while reducing and standardizing stipend compensation for all other officers. The draft compensation document is available on the website under the </span><a style="-ms-text-size-adjust:100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%;color:#007C89;font-weight:normal;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://iatse118.com/post/october-2024-general-meeting-documents"><span style="color:#0000CD;font-size:14px;"><u>October meeting materials page.</u></span></a></p></div>','user_id' => '1','count' => '1','state' => 'sent','created_at' => '2024-12-06 04:56:31','updated_at' => '2024-12-06 05:20:48'),
