-time, salaried compensation for the newly elected Business Agent, while reducing and standardizing stipend compensation for all other officers. The draft compensation document is available on the website under the </span><a style="-ms-text-size-adjust:100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%;color:#007C89;font-weight:normal;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://iatse118.com/post/october-2024-general-meeting-documents"><span style="color:#0000CD;font-size:14px;"><u>October meeting materials page.</u></span></a></p></div>','user_id' => '1','count' => '1','state' => 'sent','created_at' => '2024-12-06 04:57:36','updated_at' => '2024-12-06 05:20:49'),
            array('id' => '16','source_url' => env('APP_URL').'/message/16/nominations-for-dec-2024-118-elections-deadline-extended','subject' => 'Nominations for Dec 2024 118 Elections - Deadline extended','slug' => 'nominations-for-dec-2024-118-elections-deadline-extended','content' => '<p>Dear 118 Members,<br><br>The 2024 December General Election page is now live on the Local\'s website.<br><br>As some positions did not have nominees by the original deadline, The Executive Board has extended the nomination deadline to Dec 17th at 17:00 (5pm) for the following positions:</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;1st Member at Large (3 Year Term)<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;1 Health &amp; Welfare Trustee (4 Year Term)<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;1 Local 118 Trustee (3 Year Term)</p><p>Nomination forms can be found here.<br><br>Forms can be emailed to returningofficer@iatse118.com or mailed to the Union office at #206 - 2940 Main Street, Vancouver, BC V5T 3G3, Canada</p>','user_id' => '1','count' => '1','state' => 'sent','created_at' => '2024-12-06 04:58:49','updated_at' => '2024-12-06 05:20:49'),
            array('id' => '17','source_url' => env('APP_URL').'/message/17/nominations-for-118-elections-deadline-corrected','subject' => 'Nominations for 118 Elections - Deadline CORRECTED','slug' => 'nominations-for-118-elections-deadline-corrected','content' => '<div class="elementToProof" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:#000000;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:24px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;"><div style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:#000000;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:24px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">Dear 118 Members,</div><div style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:#000000;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:24px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">&nbsp;</div><div style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:#000000;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:24px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">I made an error in the last announcement regarding the Nomination deadline extension.&nbsp;</div><div style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:#000000;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:24px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">It would not be possible to have a 15 day balloting period in December, if nominations closed in late <i>December</i>.</div><div style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:#000000;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:24px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">My apologies for any alarm or confusion.</div><div style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:#000000;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:24px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">&nbsp;</div><div style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:#000000;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:24px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spa