s, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;line-height:24px;margin:0px 0px 0px 40px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">604-685-9553</div></div>','user_id' => '1','count' => '1','state' => 'sent','created_at' => '2024-12-06 04:59:45','updated_at' => '2024-12-06 05:20:50'),
            array('id' => '18','source_url' => env('APP_URL').'/message/18/notice-of-general-meeting-sundaynovember-24th700-pm','subject' => 'NOTICE OF GENERAL MEETING Sunday:November 24th:7:00 PM','slug' => 'notice-of-general-meeting-sundaynovember-24th700-pm','content' => '<p>The Next General Meeting of IATSE Local 118 will be held digitally Via a Zoom Webinar on<br>Sunday, November 24th @ 7:00 PM<br>Dear Brothers, Sisters, and Kin:<br><br>To ensure security, members must register in advance. You will be sent a confirmation email with the details on how to join the meeting no less than 24 hours prior to the Call to Order.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</p><p>General Meeting Agenda</p><p>On the agenda for this meeting:</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;Approval of minutes from the previous General Meeting. &nbsp;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;Reports, as outlined in the Constitution and By-Laws<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;New Business</p><p>Any members or committees with business for the agenda must submit them to office@iatse118.com 48 hours in advance of the General Meeting.</p>','user_id' => '1','count' => '1','state' => 'sent','created_at' => '2024-12-06 05:01:15','updated_at' => '2024-12-06 05:20:51'),
            array('id' => '19','source_url' => env('APP_URL').'/message/19/2025-dues-early-payment-discount','subject' => '2025 Dues Early Payment Discount','slug' => '2025-dues-early-payment-discount','content' => '<p><br>Dear Sisters, Brothers, and Kin,</p><p>Members wishing to take advantage of the 5% early payment discount for 2025 dues must pay in full before December 1st, 2024. Information on dues payments can be found here:&nbsp;</p><p>https://iatse118.com/page/paying-minimum-dues</p>','user_id' => '1','count' => '1','state' => 'sent','created_at' => '2024-12-06 05:03:39','updated_at' => '2024-12-06 05:20:52'),
            array('id' => '20','source_url' => env('APP_URL').'/message/20/reminder-notice-of-general-meeting-sundaynovember-24th700-pm','subject' => 'Reminder: NOTICE OF GENERAL MEETING Sunday:November 24th:7:00 PM','slug' => 'reminder-notice-of-general-meeting-sundaynovember-24th700-pm','content' => '<p><br>The Next General Meeting of IATSE Local 118 will be held digitally Via a Zoom Webinar on<br>Sunday, November 24th @ 7:00 PM<br>Dear Brothers, Sisters, and Kin:<br><br>To ensure security, members must register in advance. You will be sent a confirmation email with the details on how to join the meeting no less than 24 hours prior to the Call to Order.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</p><p>General Meeting Agenda</p><p>On the agenda for this meeting:</p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp;Approval of minutes from the previous General Meeting. &nbsp;<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;Reports, as outlined in the Constitution and By-Laws<br>&nbsp; &nbsp;New Business</p><p>Any members or committees with business for the agenda must submit them to office@iatse118.com 48 hours in advance of the General Meeting.<br>&nbsp;</p>','user_id' => '1','count' => '1','state' => 'sent','created_at' => '2024-12-06 05:04:49','updated_at' => '2024-12-06 05:20:52'),
            array('id' => '21','source_url' => env('APP_URL').'/message/21/updated-118-office-hours','subject' => 'Updated 118 Office Hours','slug' => 'updated-118-office-hours','content' => '<div class="elementToProof" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:black;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">Dear Sisters, Brothers, and Kin,</div><div style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:black;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">&nbsp;</div><div style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:black;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">Due to recent changes to staffing, our office will function by appointment only for the foreseeable&nbsp;future. If you need any in-person services, please reach out to <a style="-ms-text-size-adjust:100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%;color:#007C89;font-weight:normal;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;" href="mailto:office@iatse118.com" target="_blank"><u>office@iatse118.com</u></a> to arrange a time to come in.</div><div style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:black;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">&nbsp;</div><div class="elementToProof" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:black;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">During this time, email responses may be slightly delayed, and our office phone line will not be constantly monitored. Our office voicemail will be checked periodically .&nbsp;</div><div class="elementToProof" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:black;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">&nbsp;</div><div class="elementToProof" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:black;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">Please consider using email as the primary form of communication until regular office hours resume.</div><div class="elementToProof" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:black;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">&nbsp;</div><div style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:black;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">If you have any questions, please feel free to contact the board at <a style="-ms-text-size-adjust:100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%;color:#007C89;font-weight:normal;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;" href="mailto:executive@iatse118.com"><u>executive@iatse118.com</u></a>.&nbsp;</div><div style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:black;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">&nbsp;</div><div style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:black;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;margin:0px;orphans:auto;text-align:left;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">We\'ll provide a further update once regular office hours have resumed.</div>','user_id' => '1','count' => '1','state' => 'sent','created_at' => '2024-12-06 05:06:01','updated_at' => '2024-12-06 05:20:53'),
            array('id' => '22','source_url' => env('APP_URL').'/message/22/upcoming-dance-centre-calls','subject' => 'Upcoming Dance Centre Calls','slug' => 'upcoming-dance-centre-calls','content' => '<div style="text-align:left;"><div class="elementToProof" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:#000000;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:auto;text-align:start;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">Dear Members,<br><br>Dispatch will soon be sending out job offers for a show at the</div><div class="elementToProof" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:#000000;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:auto;text-align:start;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">Scotiabank Dance Centre (AKA The Dance Centre). The Dance Centre first collective agreement is in the process of being ratified, with an implementation date of Dec 1st, 2024.<br><br>Since we don\'t yet have skills lists for the Dance Centre, we will be using the GITD lists for the upcoming show.&nbsp;<br><br>The show requires one show call Head Tech ($27.03/hour) for some dates between Dec 3 and 7 and a Grip LX ($23.97/hour) for Dec 3 and 5.&nbsp;<br>&nbsp;</div><div class="elementToProof" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:#000000;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:auto;text-align:start;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">If you would&nbsp;like to receive a job offer for this upcoming show, and you are NOT on the GITD skills lists,<strong>&nbsp;text Dispatch by 3pm on Friday, November 29,&nbsp; at</strong>&nbsp;<strong>(778) 745 - 1118.</strong></div></div>','user_id' => '1','count' => '1','state' => 'sent','created_at' => '2024-12-06 05:06:57','updated_at' => '2024-12-06 05:20:54'),
            array('id' => '23','source_url' => env('APP_URL').'/message/23/dance-centre-contract-ratification-results','subject' => 'Dance Centre Contract Ratification Results','slug' => 'dance-centre-contract-ratification-results','content' => '<p><span style="font-size:16px;">Dear Sisters, Brothers, and Kin,</span><br>&nbsp;</p><div><span style="font-size:16px;">The First Collective Agreement with The Dance Centre has been ratified by the Bargaining Unit. With <strong>29 </strong>votes cast:</span><br><br><span style="font-size:16px;">28 votes in Favour</span><br><span style="font-size:16px;">0 votes Opposed</span><br><span style="font-size:16px;">1 voter Abstained.</span><br><br><span style="font-size:16px;">More Information regarding the voting process can be found here:</span><br><a style="-ms-text-size-adjust:100%;-webkit-text-size-adjust:100%;color:#007C89;font-weight:normal;mso-line-height-rule:exactly;" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://iatse118.com/post/vdc-dance-centre-society-2024-2027-ratification"><span style="font-size:16px;"><u>https://iatse118.com/post/vdc-dance-centre-society-2024-2027-ratification</u></span></a><br><br>This Collective Agreement is now in force, as of December 1st.<br><br>The organizing, BC Labour Board certification process, and bargaining for this contract was a 25 month process. Sincere thank you to all of the workers who worked together to Build Worker Power and truly ensure that Growth=Strength.<br><br>All theatrical and live performance workers in our jurisdiction deserve access to union representation and the power of collective bargaining. Together We Rise.</div>','user_id' => '1','count' => '1','state' => 'sent','created_at' => '2024-12-06 05:07:43','updated_at' => '2024-12-06 05:20:54'),
            array('id' => '24','source_url' => env('APP_URL').'/message/24/cultch-stage-contract-discussion-meeting','subject' => 'Cultch Stage Contract Discussion Meeting','slug' => 'cultch-stage-contract-discussion-meeting','content' => '<div class="elementToProof" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:#000000;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:auto;text-align:start;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">Dear 118 Members,</div><div class="elementToProof" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:#000000;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:auto;text-align:start;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">&nbsp;</div><div class="elementToProof" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:#000000;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:auto;text-align:start;text-decoration:none;text-indent:0px;text-transform:none;white-space:normal;widows:auto;word-spacing:0px;">The Union has reached a tentative deal with The Cultch for renewal of the Stage and FoH contracts.</div><div class="elementToProof" style="-webkit-text-size-adjust:auto;-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;color:#000000;font-family:Aptos, Aptos_EmbeddedFont, Aptos_MSFontService, Calibri, Helvetica, sans-serif;font-size:12pt;font-style:normal;font-variant-caps:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;orphans:auto;text-align:st